lead_paragraph: Leicester City's Premier League title dream became reality on Monday when one of the greatest sporting fairytales reached its conclusion in west London where chasing Tottenham Hotspur were held 2-2 by Chelsea.

headline.print_headline: British Soccer Team Leicester Celebrates 5,000-1 Title Success
